msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/getting_started/basics/interface/input_devices.rst:46
msgid ""
"If you use a keyboard with a non-english keyboard layout, you still may "
"benefit from switching your computer to the UK or US layout as long as you "
"work with Blender."
msgstr ""

